{"timestamp": "2025-12-11 17:37:38.304462", "event": "llm_start", "messages": "content='Based on the diagnosis report: **Anomaly**\\n\\nThe two leaf routers are connected by a point‑to‑point link (172.16.0.5/172.16.0.7) but the routing tables on both leaf routers contain **incorrect /31 routes** that point to the wrong interfaces.  \\nBecause of those wrong routes the kernel marks the destination as “Network is unreachable”, so `leaf_router_0_0` cannot reach `leaf_router_0_1` (and vice‑versa).\\n\\n**Evidence**\\n\\n| Router | Interface | IP | Routing entry for the link |\\n|--------|-----------|----|----------------------------|\\n| leaf_router_0_0 | eth0 | 172.16.0.5 | `172.16.0.0/31 dev eth0` (172.16.0.5 is not in 172.16.0.0/31) |\\n| leaf_router_0_0 | eth1 | 172.16.0.1 | `172.16.0.4/31 dev eth1` (172.16.0.1 is not in 172.16.0.4/31) |\\n| leaf_router_0_0 | eth2 | 172.16.0.3 | `172.16.0.6/31 dev eth2` (172.16.0.3 is not in 172.16.0.6/31) |\\n| leaf_router_0_1 | eth0 | 172.16.0.7 | `172.16.0.2/31 dev eth0` (172.16.0.7 is not in 172.16.0.2/31) |\\n| leaf_router_0_1 | eth1 | 172.16.0.3 | `172.16.0.8/31 dev eth1` (172.16.0.3 is not in 172.16.0.8/31) |\\n| leaf_router_0_1 | eth2 | 172.16.0.9 | `172.16.0.10/31 dev eth2` (172.16.0.9 is not in 172.16.0.10/31) |\\n\\nThe ping from `pc_0_1` to `leaf_router_0_1` succeeds, but `leaf_router_0_0` cannot ping `leaf_router_0_1` because the kernel has no valid route to 172.16.0.7.\\n\\n**Root cause**\\n\\nMis‑configured point‑to‑point routes on the leaf routers. The routes reference the wrong network prefixes for the interfaces that actually carry the link, so the kernel marks the destination as unreachable.\\n\\n**Recommendation**\\n\\nCorrect the /31 routes on both leaf routers to match the actual link IPs (or remove them if the link is not needed). After fixing the routes, the leaf routers should be able to reach each other and the network will function normally., please provide the submission. Do not submit if no report available.' additional_kwargs={} response_metadata={} id='0292c616-e8d8-4e2e-af6a-51873712116a'", "model": {"lc": 1, "type": "not_implemented", "id": ["langchain_ollama", "chat_models", "ChatOllama"], "repr": "ChatOllama(model='gpt-oss:20b', validate_model_on_init=True, temperature=0.0, base_url='http://10.68.186.140:11434')", "name": "ChatOllama"}}
